{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/JS-bit-operator/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Discreater Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"de43a1d4-ba95-595d-893e-0b5f8d201931","excerpt":"最近刷leetcode的时候，碰到要处理上边界()和下边界()的情况，这时候想当然地用了移位操作符来计算2的幂次，本以为js的number类型上限应该大于32位，但是实际情况并不是和想象中的一样，先看结果： 1左移31位变成了负数，出现这种情况是因为js的按位操作符是将操作数看作32位来计算，结果也是3…","html":"<p>最近刷leetcode的时候，碰到要处理<code class=\"language-text\">int</code>上边界(<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>31</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2^{31}-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.897438em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span>)和下边界(<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>31</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">-2^{31}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.897438em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">3</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>)的情况，这时候想当然地用了移位操作符<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;&lt;</code>来计算2的幂次，本以为js的number类型上限应该大于32位，但是实际情况并不是和想象中的一样，先看结果：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">31</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2147483648</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// -2^31</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">1073741824</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 2^30</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">31</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2147483648</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">31</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">2147483648</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">32</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">1</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>1左移31位变成了负数，出现这种情况是因为js的按位操作符是<strong>将操作数看作32位来计算</strong>，结果也是32位的形式。\n下面是<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Bitwise_Operators#Summary\">MDN的官方解释</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>按位操作符（Bitwise operators）</strong> 将其操作数（operands）当作32位的比特序列（由0和1组成），而不是十进制、十六进制或八进制数值。例如，十进制数9，用二进制表示则为1001。按位操作符操作数字的二进制形式，但是返回值依然是标准的JavaScript数值。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>顺便推荐一波<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/27662366\">进阶的解决办法</a>，来自知乎的ice1000</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"JS 按位操作符溢出问题","date":"2020-03-14"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/JS-bit-operator/","previous":null,"next":null}}}